{"tid":464875,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件你人生中最撚後悔嘅事","createTime":"2017-11-11T03:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T06:15:53.000Z","uid":138834,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"562da6a2c189a1027d3cc2ca1cd2c8f53074e13c","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"細個時(4歲左近)老母帶我出街，咁當年住旺角，就好多周街行嘅個身又好污糟嘅露宿者<br />\n<br />\n我就問我老母佢地係咩人嚟，我老母就話<br />\n佢地係傻佬嚟架，唔好行埋去<br />\n<br />\n然後行到路口，等過馬路時突然見到對面有個露宿者等過馬路<br />\n<br />\n我就忍唔住大聲叫左出嚟<br />\n<br />\n哇!傻佬呀！<br />\n<br />\n之後我老母就好驚咁拉住我走左，冇過條馬路<br />\n我仲記得有回頭望個露宿者，佢都冇過馬路，企係到等到個綠燈完左都冇過<br />\n<br />\n後尾大個左，成日諗返起件事真係好撚內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到今時今日廿幾歲都仲會成日諗起<br />\n<br />\n講真，後悔過$6usd時放哂啲Bitcoin<br />\n後悔過我唔睇天氣報告就揸帆船出海撞正暴風雨<br />\n後悔過唔查清路線就行山而遇難<br />\n後悔過以前講啲悔氣說話hurt鳩屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都唔知點解會咁<br />\n<br />\n自認份人係偏自戀同自我中心<br />\n唯獨依件事不停激發啲自我厭惡出嚟<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有時光機"},{"pid":"3c6beb1fb069a17e34e25284dc9b572adb10b63e","tid":464875,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"出世"},{"pid":"589f0bdd03b6c8a7af21ffa61a532b6754ab01de","tid":464875,"uid":2463,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"你咁樣都死唔去都算命大"},{"pid":"3acf12945a39b918a28d67914b90cf248dbf62f4","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁樣都死唔去都算命大</blockquote><br />\n你指咩，啲遇難？"},{"pid":"71f1ad854f86c4b9fc34bda4d2c3d5cf148ea4c5","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出世</blockquote><br />\n都唔到你選擇，有咩好後悔"},{"pid":"e05e91a97f7496b5471548136992065bac06316b","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaba633e7846f4ffd6c732339832f96d0439aa2a","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6893e619be775a73bf4139074141e97051b150","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331938dd606abe14a7176b164c821aeccfa189e7","tid":464875,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:45:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7281d44d62b61e21021bb397f73b6df827259eb9","tid":464875,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫遇難"},{"pid":"ba674d4c58d52bc40a4d495b8691ac21520db115","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知唔知咩叫遇難</blockquote><br />\n依個問題你要問返自己<br />\n<br />\n解釋：<br />\n遭到災難。《史記．卷四七．孔子世家》：「吾昔從夫子遇難於匡，今又遇難於此，命也已。」<br />\n相似詞：\t罹難、遭災、遇害"},{"pid":"44b2c1de9c06bf3aed7d4ffa81a68f4d238bbfcd","tid":464875,"uid":75636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:51:41.000Z","msg":"無 all in700"},{"pid":"dddd65d5f294f9bf04df04f987c8421d0b83f2cc","tid":464875,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"最後悔識左你"},{"pid":"36c69f107b47bb5372a90ec859cce122892b3ce5","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後悔識左你</blockquote><br />\n你無識過我"},{"pid":"2724d2bb7bbaa35e74863cd751288c4cdd93c1ff","tid":464875,"uid":59465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"真心<br />\n係你老母唔識教仔<br />\n唔關你事"},{"pid":"a35478231e330b0977f6478fc8a4c28f8b7021a4","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無 all in700</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉屌，當年讀書出嚟打散工時貪玩買左50個Bitcoin，當年升左兩倍就放左仲以為自己賺好多好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n揸到今日夠比首期"},{"pid":"158e406ec057f2121f9f6b79ced767ba6386b8a2","tid":464875,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心<br />\n係你老母唔識教仔<br />\n唔關你事</blockquote><br />\n我知，所以我同我老母關係好差<br />\n但做件事嘅終究係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85055d5a21ead3230a0c5447d562cfca4fb59c62","tid":464875,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心<br />\n係你老母唔識教仔<br />\n唔關你事</blockquote><br />\n我知，所以我同我老母關係好差<br />\n但做件事嘅終究係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n童言無忌啫<br />\n你一直記住 係好事嚟<br />\n第時你咪識點教啲仔女<br />\n人就係咁樣走落嚟<br />\n一路進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f36ea01a6e7c5e12f39898f4ba9f357c273b50","tid":464875,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後悔識左你</blockquote><br />\n你無識過我</blockquote><br />\n唔係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101e5c4e5dbc7e25e6abe6d83551a8fa4994f08d","tid":464875,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出世</blockquote><br />\nX2"}]}